	                          Sub0001_Ses1_bld002_rest.nii.gz, the BOLD_stem will be _rest.
	                          This input file should be stored in 
	                          <subject_dir>/<subject_id>/bold/<run_number>/
	                         
OPTIONAL ARGUMENTS:
